  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether aerosolized vancomycin is effective in the
      treatment of methicillin-resistant staphylococcus aureus pneumonia under mechanical
      ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
